The foldable seats in the third row free up more packing space for everything you need to take with you. Both the second and third row seats can be adjusted into an array of configurations to accommodate different passenger and luggage needs.

Once you are on the road in the Ertiga, the responsiveness of the engine is the perfect assurance that the road ahead is well worth the time spent travelling.
